Package: uptime-monitor
Version: 1.0.0
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, python3-venv, sqlite3
Maintainer: Yaroslav Andreichuk <yaroslav.andreichuk@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/ajjs1ajjs/Uptime-Monitor-APP
Description: Website uptime monitoring service
 Uptime Monitor is a FastAPI-based service for monitoring
 website availability with notifications via Telegram,
 Email, Slack, Discord, and more.
 .
 Features:
  - Monitor multiple websites
  - SSL certificate expiration tracking
  - Multi-channel notifications
  - Web-based dashboard
  - REST API
  - Systemd service integration
